name: UGABusTracker
0:
”Alexa, ask Bus Tracker how long for the next Milledge bus?”
”Alexa, ask Bus Tracker when is the next Milledge Night bus?”
”Alexa, ask Bus Tracker how long until the next Health Sciences bus?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: bus tracker
des: The UGA Bus Tracker uses The University of Georgia's publicly-available bus location data to provide real-time bus route updates. Using live data updates, you can quickly ask about the next bus arriving on the Milledge, Health Sciences, or Milledge Night routes.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
